libminesweeper
------------------------------------------
Library for handling Minesweeper game logic

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.1-1
  libminesweeper-devel-3.0.0-1bl1
  libminesweeper3-3.0.0-1bl1
  pkg-config-2.4.3-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.44-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  gcc-g++-12.4.0-3
  ninja-1.12.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/joelekstrom/libminesweeper

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/joelekstrom/libminesweeper/archive/refs/tags/v3.0.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libminesweeper-3.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libminesweeper-3.0.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libminesweeper-3.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libminesweeper-3.0.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libminesweeper3-3.0.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libminesweeper-devel-3.0.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libminesweeper)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libminesweeper.README
  /usr/share/doc/libminesweeper/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/libminesweeper/README.md

(libminesweeper3)
  /usr/bin/cygminesweeper-3.dll

(libminesweeper-devel)
  /usr/include/minesweeper.h
  /usr/include/minesweeper.hpp
  /usr/lib/libminesweeper.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libminesweeper.pc

------------------

Port Notes:

